702388f-a.title: Brooklyn: 5th Avenue - 4th Street
702388f-a.text:
5th Avenue, north from Fourth Street, underneath the B.M.T. elevated. Note the stairway to the"El" station, at Third Street. View 2 shows the "El" station at Third Street, seen across the James J.Byrne Memorial Park and Playground at the N.W. corner
of Fifth Avenue and Fourth Street.
P.L. Sperr  June 14, 1940
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
